{{vgname|杀出重围：陨落|en=Deus Ex: The Fall|cn=杀出重围：陨落|tw=駭客入侵：隕落}}是[[赛博朋克|赛博朋克]][[动作角色扮演游戏|动作角色扮演]][[隐蔽类游戏|隐蔽类]]电子游戏，为[[杀出重围系列|杀出重围系列]]的第四作。游戏为系列首次登上移动电话平台，情节则和2011年游戏《[[駭客入侵：人類革命|杀出重围：人类革命]]》紧密相关。

== 设定 ==
{{Deus Ex编年史}}
游戏设定于2027年，情节围绕着玩家角色本·萨克松——一名增强佣兵，原属于英国[[特种空勤团|特种空勤团]]。情节直接延续詹姆斯·斯沃洛《[[駭客入侵：人類革命|杀出重围：人类革命]]》——2011年游戏《杀出重围：人类革命》的一本搭配小说<ref>{{Cite news |first=Wesley |last=Yin-Poole |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-06-05-deus-ex-the-fall-is-an-iphone-and-ipad-game-out-soon |title=Deus Ex: The Fall is an iPhone and iPad game out soon |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2013-06-05 |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-date=2013-07-21 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6IHiY5IqA?url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-06-05-deus-ex-the-fall-is-an-iphone-and-ipad-game-out-soon |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 开发 ==
游戏由[[Eidos蒙特利尔|Eidos蒙特利尔]]和[[N-Fusion|N-Fusion]]开发。Eidos蒙特利尔的《杀出重围：人类革命》设计原始理念，并同N-Fusion团队合作，而Jean-François Dugas再次监督此游戏。游戏使用[[Unity_(游戏引擎)|Unity]]引擎<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.siliconera.com/2013/06/11/eidos-montreal-tells-us-all-about-deus-ex-the-fall/ |title=Eidos Montreal Tells Us All About Deus Ex: The Fall |publisher=Siliconera |date=2013-06-11 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2016-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160225135030/http://www.siliconera.com/2013/06/11/eidos-montreal-tells-us-all-about-deus-ex-the-fall/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 发行 ==

在2013年4月，史克威尔将短语“杀出重围：陨落”登记为商标，并注册了相关域名<ref>{{Cite news |first=Sinan |last=Kubba |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/03/06/deus-ex-the-fall-trademarked-while-human-defiance-points-towar/ |title=Deus Ex: The Fall trademarked, while Human Defiance points toward film |publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]] |date=2013-03-06 |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128191713/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/03/06/deus-ex-the-fall-trademarked-while-human-defiance-points-towar/ |archive-date=2015-01-28 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。在2013年6月上旬，《杀出重围：陨落》开发者[[Eidos蒙特利尔|Eidos蒙特利尔]]在官方[[Twitter|Twitter]]发布了一条微博，其中展示了含有游戏名称的预告片<ref>{{Cite news |first=Luke |last=Karmali |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/04/deus-ex-the-fall-teased-by-eidos-montreal |title=Deus Ex: The Fall Teased by Eidos Montreal |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]] |date=2013-06-04 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2013-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607224002/https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/04/deus-ex-the-fall-teased-by-eidos-montreal |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年6月5日，史克威尔艾尼克斯宣布《杀出重围：陨落》将于夏季在[[iOS|iOS]]平台发行，之后还将发行[[Android|Android]]版<ref>{{Cite news |first=Valerie |last=Bourdeau |url=http://community.eidosmontreal.com/blogs/Deus-Ex-The-Fall-Announced |title=Announcing Deus Ex: The Fall |publisher=Eidos Montreal |date=2013-06-07 |accessdate=2013-07-09 |archive-date=2014-09-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920232555/http://community.eidosmontreal.com/blogs/Deus-Ex-The-Fall-Announced |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。史克威尔艾尼克斯在2013年6月的{{link-en|电子娱乐博览会|Electronic Entertainment Expo 2013}}展示了游戏，并还发布了游戏玩法影片和截图<ref>{{Cite news |first=Mike |last=Schramm |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/07/deus-ex-the-fall-is-a-cyber-renaissance-faire-for-touchscreens/ |title=Deus Ex: The Fall is a cyber Renaissance faire for touchscreens |publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]] |date=2013-06-07 |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130609000255/http://www.joystiq.com/2013/06/07/deus-ex-the-fall-is-a-cyber-renaissance-faire-for-touchscreens/ |archive-date=2013-06-09 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。史克威尔艾尼克斯在7月上旬宣布，iOS版将于2013年7月11日在全球发行<ref name="release date">{{Cite news |first=Alexander |last=Sliwinski |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/07/08/deus-ex-the-fall-lands-july-11/ |title=Deus Ex: The Fall lands July 11 |publisher=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]] |date=2013-07-08 |accessdate=2013-06-09 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6JGt831ym?url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/07/08/deus-ex-the-fall-lands-july-11/ |archive-date=2013-08-31 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。PC版於之後宣布，2014年3月25日發佈在[[Steam|Steam]]<ref>{{Cite web |first=Phil |last=Savage |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2014/02/25/deus-ex-the-fall-announced-for-pc-release/ |title=Deus Ex: The Fall announced for PC release |work=[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] |date=2014-02-24 |accessdate=2014-05-24 |archive-date=2016-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503105016/http://www.pcgamer.com/deus-ex-the-fall-announced-for-pc-release/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

