《杀出重围：陨落》获得媒体从积极到褒贬不一的评价。其在评论聚合网站Metacritic上获得69/100的汇总得分<ref name="MetaReview" />。

IGN的贾斯汀·戴维斯给游戏打了8/10分，称赞了游戏的情节、感官、探索与流线型的建构，但批评了糟糕的战斗。在结语中，他称“除了令人沮丧的战斗，其成功几乎令人震惊。《陨落》将杀出重围的核心经验提炼至移动设备上。将神秘而讲述精彩的剧情，强力的新增稳定流线，以及令人印象深刻的游戏世界全部结合，而制作的手机体验，当我开始后便不想放下了”<ref name="IGN" />。

手机游戏专门站点Touch Arcade给了游戏非常高的4.5/5星级<ref name="TouchArcade">{{cite web|url=http://toucharcade.com/2013/07/10/deus-ex-the-fall-review-console-gaming-stuffed-into-a-mobile-package/|title='Deus Ex: The Fall' Review - Console Gaming Stuffed into a Mobile Package|author=Jared Nelson|publisher=Touch Arcade|date=2013-06-10|accessdate=11-07-2013|archive-date=2013-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130713084347/http://toucharcade.com/2013/07/10/deus-ex-the-fall-review-console-gaming-stuffed-into-a-mobile-package/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。站点对游戏发行于iOS而非PC或游戏机表示批评，但也称游戏质量高、用户体验良好：“其在故事、制作效果和视觉方面散发着‘游戏机的品质’，它正好值得去玩”。

《[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]》的克里斯汀·多兰给了游戏很低的5/10分，批评游戏崩溃错误、糟糕的战斗和控制、重复的图形、不牢靠的剧情和配音员，但他仍然称赞了触屏功能和大体气氛<!-- He finished saying: "It's ''Deus Ex'' in cross-section, but although so many of the right pieces are in place, the energy and skill that usually brings the whole thing to life is missing". --><ref name="EuroReview" />。

Digital Spy给了游戏5星中的3星，称“《杀出重围：陨落》虽短，但对于《杀出重围：人类革命》爱好者是甜美的衍生品，在下载之前，你只需保证仔细检查你的iOS设备固件和硬件”<ref name="DigiSpy">{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/review/a496775/deus-ex-the-fall-review-iphone-a-faithful-but-broken-spin-off.html|title='Deus Ex: The Fall' review (iPhone): A faithful but broken spin-off|author=Scott Nichols|publisher=Digital Spy|date=2013-06-11|accessdate=11-07-2013|archive-date=2013-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130713235922/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/gaming/review/a496775/deus-ex-the-fall-review-iphone-a-faithful-but-broken-spin-off.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在游戏发行后发现，游戏拒绝让[[iOS越狱|越狱]]设备玩家使用火器功能，这在游戏社区内引发一些争议<ref name="PolygonJailbreak">{{cite web|url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/7/11/4515082/deus-ex-the-fall-jailbroken-ios-devices-guns-disabled|title=Deus Ex: The Fall disables firing guns on jailbroken iOS devices|author=Samit Sarkar|publisher=Polygon|date=2013-07-11|accessdate=11-07-2013|archive-date=2013-10-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131028100013/http://www.polygon.com/2013/7/11/4515082/deus-ex-the-fall-jailbroken-ios-devices-guns-disabled|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="MacruJailbreak">{{cite web|url=http://www.macrumors.com/2013/07/11/deus-ex-the-fall-prevents-players-with-jailbroken-ios-devices-from-firing-guns/|title='Deus Ex: The Fall' Prevents Players With Jailbroken iOS Devices From Firing Guns|author=Jordan Golson|publisher=MacRumors|date=2013-07-11|accessdate=11-07-2013|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111212709/https://www.macrumors.com/2013/07/11/deus-ex-the-fall-prevents-players-with-jailbroken-ios-devices-from-firing-guns/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。史克威尔随后确认了问题，并发行了问题修正补丁<ref>David Hinkle (Jul 12, 2013). [http://www.joystiq.com/2013/07/12/deus-ex-the-fall-update-will-unjam-guns-on-jailbroken-ios-devic/ "Deus Ex: The Fall update will unjam guns on jailbroken iOS devices"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2013/07/12/deus-ex-the-fall-update-will-unjam-guns-on-jailbroken-ios-devic/ |date=20150128193010 }}. Joystiq. Retrieved 12-07-2013.</ref><ref>{{cite_web|url=http://community.eidosmontreal.com/blogs/Deus-Ex-The-Fall-Patch-Release|title=Deus Ex: The Fall Patch Live NOW!|last=Badke|first=Adam|publisher=Eidos Montreal|date=2013-07-17|accessdate=2018-08-26|language=zh|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180826025323/http://community.eidosmontreal.com/blogs/Deus-Ex-The-Fall-Patch-Release|archivedate=2018-08-26}}</ref>

=== PC版本 ===
PC版本的《杀出重围：陨落》整體評價不理想，Metacritic的評分為45/100<ref name="MetaReviewPC"/>。

[[IGN|IGN]]評論員Craig Pearson給予遊戲3/10, 批評遊戲在電腦上的適應不良，尤其是缺乏跳躍鍵，無力控制幾何變換和遊戲沒完全地反應選單操作與按鈕壓力的問題。他總結，“在糟糕控制和系統bug的掙扎下，如果堅持住的话，玩家可以潛行通风管道，駭入电子邮件，把敌人和自己搞的晕头转向。如果制作得更用心一些的话，这原本是PC平台上的闪亮大作”<ref name="IGNrevPC">{{cite_web| url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/24/deus-ex-the-fall-pc-review| title=Deus Ex: The Fall PC Review: The Fail| last=Pearson| first=Craig| publisher=IGN| date=2014-03-24| accessdate=2014-05-24| archive-date=2014-04-12| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140412072559/http://www.ign.com/articles/2014/03/24/deus-ex-the-fall-pc-review| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]評論員Andy Kelly給予遊戲40/100的分數, 稱《杀出重围：陨落》“真的是我玩過最爛的PC版遊戲。”部分原因在於遊戲反應遲鈍的控制，尤其是在選單上<ref name="PCGamer">{{cite_web| url=http://www.pcgamer.com/review/deus-ex-the-fall-review/| title=Deus Ex: The Fall Review| last=Kelly| first=Andy| date=2014-04-25| publisher=PC Gamer| accessdate=2014-05-24| archive-date=2014-04-25| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140425221010/http://www.pcgamer.com/review/deus-ex-the-fall-review/| dead-url=no}}</ref>。

